    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>德尔塔粒子</strong> 是<strong>《半条命1》</strong>的<strong>单人游戏模组</strong>。<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/da170111cc154ad9750285f68dc78c79.poster.avif?t=1752438215\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/da170111cc154ad9750285f68dc78c79.webm?t=1752438215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/da170111cc154ad9750285f68dc78c79.mp4?t=1752438215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情发生在《半条命1》的世界观中。你将扮演错综复杂的&quot;德尔塔基地&quot;的技术工程师尼克-法瑞尔。不幸的是，主角在错误的时间出现在了错误的地点，因为黑山基地研究设施的一次实验产生了串联共振，将外星生物从Xen世界传送到了地球。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/c4e24f91cf3a9f96b4172a58a364ba21.poster.avif?t=1752438215\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/c4e24f91cf3a9f96b4172a58a364ba21.webm?t=1752438215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/c4e24f91cf3a9f96b4172a58a364ba21.mp4?t=1752438215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>新的单人战役由4个章节组成，包含35张地图</strong><br>这是一个很长的单人战役，<i> </i>长达3到6小时。新的故事、角色和冒险正等待着你的到来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/f90297683ae8ebe2d5074de1685bbc33.poster.avif?t=1752438215\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/f90297683ae8ebe2d5074de1685bbc33.webm?t=1752438215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/f90297683ae8ebe2d5074de1685bbc33.mp4?t=1752438215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>全面改造，拥有大量新内容</strong><br>包含新的纹理、音效、模型和其他资产。 <strong>德尔塔粒子 </strong>完全基于新的资产！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/b4654f48ea76fcfe653e004b0ccad615.poster.avif?t=1752438215\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/b4654f48ea76fcfe653e004b0ccad615.webm?t=1752438215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/b4654f48ea76fcfe653e004b0ccad615.mp4?t=1752438215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>新的科研综合体 &quot;德尔塔基地&quot;的环境氛围</strong><br>位于内华达沙漠某处的全新科研综合体。因为美国政府已经拨款开发空间传送装置，&quot;德尔塔基地&quot;成为了<br>黑山基地在实验性传送研究方面的主要竞争对手。 <br>探访新的地点，从科学实验室到工业区！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/b6e3fd8cd988189f5954bf27758af2a7.poster.avif?t=1752438215\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/b6e3fd8cd988189f5954bf27758af2a7.webm?t=1752438215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/b6e3fd8cd988189f5954bf27758af2a7.mp4?t=1752438215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>全新的武器</strong><br>你的武器库包含了新武器和经过大量改装的旧武器。现在你肯定已经全副武装起来了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/710a4d739d673a62f3cf9e83eb3c1952.poster.avif?t=1752438215\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/710a4d739d673a62f3cf9e83eb3c1952.webm?t=1752438215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707900/extras/710a4d739d673a62f3cf9e83eb3c1952.mp4?t=1752438215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>全新暗黑氛围背景音乐</strong><br>它采用了由 &quot;<strong>Iron Cthulhu Apocalypse</strong>&quot;和&quot;<strong>Out of Hell</strong>&quot;制作的全新黑暗环境背景音乐。这些音乐让你沉浸在这些地方深沉阴郁的氛围之中。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>XEN 地图</strong><br>这里有XEN。如果你喜欢这个来自半条命世界观的外星岩石世界，那么你一定会喜欢它！</p></li></ul>",
